    <title>TVBox播放器内置接口教程</title>
    <url>/2022/07/06/TVBox%E6%92%AD%E6%94%BE%E5%99%A8%E5%86%85%E7%BD%AE%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%A3%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>手机打开MT管理器</p>
<p>用MT打开TVBox软件</p>
<p><img src="/../images/TVBox%E6%92%AD%E6%94%BE%E5%99%A8%E5%86%85%E7%BD%AE%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%A3%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20220706085435.jpg"></p>
<span id="more"></span>

<p><img src="/../images/TVBox%E6%92%AD%E6%94%BE%E5%99%A8%E5%86%85%E7%BD%AE%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%A3%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/11.jpg" alt="11"></p>
<p>点击classes.dex文件</p>
<p><img src="/../images/TVBox%E6%92%AD%E6%94%BE%E5%99%A8%E5%86%85%E7%BD%AE%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%A3%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/12.jpg" alt="12"></p>
<p>点击Dex编辑器++</p>
<p><img src="/../images/TVBox%E6%92%AD%E6%94%BE%E5%99%A8%E5%86%85%E7%BD%AE%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%A3%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/13.jpg" alt="13"></p>
<p>点击搜索</p>
<p>发起新搜索</p>
<p><img src="/../images/TVBox%E6%92%AD%E6%94%BE%E5%99%A8%E5%86%85%E7%BD%AE%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%A3%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/14.jpg" alt="14"></p>
<p>搜索里输入<br>const-string v5</p>
<p><img src="/../images/TVBox%E6%92%AD%E6%94%BE%E5%99%A8%E5%86%85%E7%BD%AE%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%A3%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/15.jpg" alt="15"></p>
<p>搜索出来的比较多<br>要找这个文件夹下的</p>
<p>com.github.tvbox.osc.ui.activity</p>
<p>【HomeActivity】<br>下面</p>
<p>【const-stringv5，””】</p>
<p><img src="/../images/TVBox%E6%92%AD%E6%94%BE%E5%99%A8%E5%86%85%E7%BD%AE%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%A3%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/16.jpg" alt="16"></p>
<p>找到<br>const-stringv5，””</p>
<p>在””里填上你的接口</p>
<p><img src="/../images/TVBox%E6%92%AD%E6%94%BE%E5%99%A8%E5%86%85%E7%BD%AE%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%A3%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/18.jpg" alt="18"></p>
<p>点击保存<br>返回签名<br>安装<br>就可以实现了<br>内置接口</p>
<p><img src="/../images/TVBox%E6%92%AD%E6%94%BE%E5%99%A8%E5%86%85%E7%BD%AE%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%A3%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/17.jpg" alt="17"></p>
<p>本次教程结束</p>
]]></content>
